得出结论，该演员<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/matthew-perrys-cause-of-death-ruled-as-acute-effects-of-ketamine-3559713">死于“氯胺酮的急性作用”</a> 。</p><p>本月早些时候，有报道称佩里<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/matthew-perry-threw-table-at-ex-fiancee-molly-hurwitz-report-claims-3569906">对至少两名女性进行了人身攻击，并在死亡前谎称自己清醒</a>。其中一项指控据称与他在 2021 年指控他出轨后向前未婚妻莫莉·赫维茨“扔咖啡桌”有关<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/friends-cast-saddened-by-claims-matthew-perry-assaulted-women-3575767">。据说其他演员对这些报道感到“压力和悲伤”</a> 。</p><p>最近有报道称， <i>《老友记》</i>的演员们计划在艾美奖上举行<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/friends-cast-reportedly-planning-special-reunion-to-honour-matthew-perry-3542707">一次特别重聚，以纪念佩里</a>，但这<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/heres-why-the-planned-emmys-tribute-to-matthew-perry-was-cancelled-3573114">并没有如愿</a>。</p><p> “我们很早就讨论过这个问题，”执行制片人杰西·柯林斯说。 “但我可以想象，从他们的角度来看，他们正在哀悼与他们仍然非常亲近的人。</p><p> “我不能代表他们说话，但我们都必须尊重他们是自己的家人。可能只是有点太早了。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/friends-fans-delighted-as-cast-members-reunite-twice-in-the-same-week-3583408">《老友记》的粉丝们因剧组成员在同一周内两次重聚而感到高兴的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
观看 Soulwax 在 2024 年英国和欧洲巡演中首次亮相新歌和史诗般的舞台表演https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-soulwax-debut-new-songs-and-epic-stage-show-on-2024-uk-and-european-tour-3582723?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=watch-soulwax-debut-new-songs-and-epic-stage-show-on-2024-uk-and-european-tourAndrew Trendell Tue, 06 Feb 2024 20:04:12 +0000 Music NewsNewsElectronic https://www.nme.com/?p=3582723 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Soulwax 现场表演的 Stephen Dewaele 和 David Dewaele，2024 年（摄影：Mariano Regidor/Redferns）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>舞曲摇滚偶像们带着黑暗的新氛围、三位鼓手和他们下一张专辑的品尝者回归</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-soulwax-debut-new-songs-and-epic-stage-show-on-2024-uk-and-european-tour-3582723">Watch Soulwax 在 2024 年英国和欧洲巡演中首次亮相的新歌和史诗般的舞台表演</a>首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上出现。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Soulwax 现场表演的 Stephen Dewaele 和 David Dewaele，2024 年（摄影：Mariano Regidor/Redferns）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/SOULWAX">Soulwax</a>在最近的 2024 年英国和欧洲巡演中首次推出了新材料以及雄心勃勃的舞台表演。查看下面的镜头和照片。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/2manydjs-david-bowie-heard-on-radio-soulwax-trash-remix-3358980">2ManyDJs – “David Bowie 曾经在我们的网络论坛上发帖”</a></strong></li></ul><p>比利时舞蹈朋克偶像们五年来首次进行现场表演，为期 13 场的演出从欧洲大陆拉开帷幕，然后于周末登陆英国。</p><p> <em>NME</em>参加了周五（2 月 2 日）在伦敦 The Roundhouse 举行的伦敦约会，Dewaele 兄弟得到了一场大型新现场制作的支持，并加入了一支由三名鼓手和其他一些合成器和吉他音乐家组成的乐队。</p><p>虽然打击乐三人组是乐队之前为支持前作专辑《From Deewee》和《Essential》而进行的巡回演出的重演，但这一次，电子先驱们在一场更具赛博朋克风格的演出中将白色服装换成了全黑服装，这与对旧材料的诠释和新歌曲的播出感觉。 </p><figure id="attachment_3582726" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3582726" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3582726" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_2.jpg" alt="Soulwax 的 Stephen Dewaele 和 David Dewaele，2024 年现场演出（摄影：Mariano Regidor/Redferns）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3582726" class="wp-caption-text"> Soulwax 的 Stephen Dewaele 和 David Dewaele，2024 年现场演出（摄影：Mariano Regidor/Redferns） </figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3582727" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3582727" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3582727" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_3.jpg" alt="Soulwax 乐队的布莱克·戴维斯 (Blake Davies) 与 Soulwax 合作演出（摄影：Mariano Regidor/Redferns）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/soulwax_2024_2000_3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3582727" class="wp-caption-text"> Soulwax 乐队的布莱克·戴维斯 (Blake Davies) 与 Soulwax 合作演出（摄影：Mariano Regidor/Redferns）</figcaption></figure><p>新歌“Hot Like Sahara”被用来作为开场曲，让人想起乐队早期作品的摇滚倾向，然后呈现出更加黑暗和科幻的戏剧性转变。其他播出的新材料包括偏执的后朋克债务“Idiots In Love”、激进的合成锐舞摇滚“New Earth Time”以及令人欣喜的中场休息“Polaris”。</p><p>在下面观看新歌曲和整个巡演的片段。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="SOULWAX-像撒哈拉一样热（新歌）在 poppodium 013 Tilburg 演奏" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3o30iuP-9zk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="SOULWAX @ Paradiso，2024 年 1 月 15 日：新地球时间，另一个借口" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/JMKBUGax-OU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Soulwax -- 总是二元/Krack/Polaris -- 马德里 -- 2024.01.23" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/axqsL1TlaxU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C2-D6e_ozjU/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.